  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will evaluate the efficiency of a pharmacist-anesthesiologist collaboration
      in the anesthetic consultation in the prevention of medical errors perioperatively in
      patients undergoing scheduled surgery
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
